        <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
          <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-accent"></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Mathematics</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li>Scored in the top 5% in 2023 AMC 12</li>
            <li>Received Honorable Mention Award in the 2023 HiMCM</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

