          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Robotics (FRC Team Golem 6706)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">Leader of the robotics team during 11th grade</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            <li><strong>2024:</strong> Innovation in Control Award (Iowa Regional), 1st Prize in WRC (Beijing)</li>
            <li><strong>2025:</strong> Quality Award (Shanghai Regional), Autonomous Award & Regional Finalists (Colorado Regional)</li>
            <li>Qualified for FIRST Championship, Johnson Division</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm">
            <a href="https://golem6706-shenzhen.github.io/golem6706-shenzhen/" class="text-accent hover:underline">View Team Website</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
